{"title":"轻轻拿起话筒……","authors":["陈志铭"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":1,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻拿起话筒……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈志铭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去年，厦门市成为我国第一个使用万门程控电话城市。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻拿起话筒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只听见低唤频频，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直接拨号吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半分钟——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和香港挂通。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界一下子变小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时间套上了缰笼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我的话声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在太平洋上来去匆匆——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不久将来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从华盛顿直拨厦门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从厦门直拨东京……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向世界畅开心胸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让生活添几分笑容。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"话筒握在手中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"止不住心海波动："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喂——喂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信息时代吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要跟上你的行踪！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}